 style=3D"color: #1a1a1a; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 1=
em 0;"><span>COVID was and remains terrible [insert all of the bad things],=
 but there was something catalyzing about the early days of the pandemic. I=
n </span><em><a href=3D"https://substack.com/redirect/4e4021ce-01dd-471d-9e=
